title: Live The Search Europe - Part 5 - Portugal
description:
Jayce Robinson and Lyndon Wake continue their southbound voyage through Europe. This fragment of the trip sees them explore the Portuguese coast. 

They have already travelled the coast of Ireland, United Kingdom, France and Spain in search for new hidden spots and waves that are foreseen as cold and stormy monsters. 

Here is the last part of their trip.

Music: 

"Winter" by BREE TRANTER
"Disco fever" by GOAT
"Wounded Love" by BREE TRANTER

Film & Edit by Luke Pilbeam
Additional footage by Tomas Paivaraposo
